passages.text:
The window looks out across a wild, rocky vista. Even if Thaxted could climb through he would plunge hundreds of feet to his doom.

(Hmmm? There's a jolly thought!)
{
(Set:$windowflag to false)
}
[[Back|Locked Room]]

The lamp is very loosely fixed to the wall. A strong smell of gas emanates from it. There's a leak somewhere although the flame burns enough to light the room.
{
(Set:$lampflag to false)
}
[[Back|Locked Room]]

The mattress is damp and has a grubby sheet rolled up as an improvised pillow. There are bloodstains from Thaxted's nose.

(Not exactly the Ritz, Thaxted, old chap...)
{
(Set:$bedflag to false)
}
[[Back|Locked Room]]

Unable to resist the temptation, Thaxted pokes the mattress. The fragile material splits and a multicoloured head pops out.

The bug's head is as big as Thaxted's thumb nail and he is reknowned for his large thumbs!!!

Fortunately, the bug's body is too big to squeeze through the hole in the mattress... For the time being...
{
{
(Set:$bugflag to false)
}
}
Involuntarilly shuddering, [[Thaxted thinks again...|What To Do]]

This the right hand corridor. All righty...

{(if: not $GuardsScared and $GuardFlag)[(set: $GuardsScared to true)[
"Reckon he's scampered off down this corridor," says a guard. "Well, I won't be following him down there... The Baron doesn't like peoplr sneaking into his rooms... Zoltan will take care of him..."
]]}

[[BACK|Corridor Room]]

[[Continue down the corridor.|FRCorridor1]]

{
(if: $GuardFlag)[
(if: not $Hidden)[
(set: $GuardCount to $GuardCount-1)[
(if: $GuardCount is 0)[
(go-to: "Guards Catch You")
]
]
]
]
}

{<font color = "red" size = "6">
(print: "Thaxted's Stamina " + (text: $MyStamina) + " Zoltan's Stamina " + (text: $ZoltanStamina))
</font>}

(either: "Zoltan balls his hand into a huge fist and brings it crashing down onto Thaxted's head...","Zoltan raises a big boot and kicks Thaxted in the stomach...","Zoltan smacks Thaxted...","Zoltan punches Thaxted on the chin...")
{
(if: $MyStamina is 0)[
(go-to: "Beaten By Zoltan")
]
}
[[Keep fighting...|Fight Zoltan]]

{<font color = "red" size = "6">
(print: "Thaxted's Stamina " + (text: $MyStamina) + " Zoltan's Stamina  " + (text: $ZoltanStamina))
</font>}

{(either: "Thaxted gives Zoltan a damn good biff...","Thaxted slaps the big fellow around the chops...","Thaxted delivers a jolly good roundhouse kick to the guts...","Thaxted feints to his right and socks Zoltan with a short punch to the chin...")

(if: $Attack > 1)[
And catches him with his (if: $PoisonKnife)[poisoned ]knife...
]

(if: $ZoltanStamina < 1)[
(go-to: "Beat Zoltan")
]}

[[Keep fighting|Fight Zoltan]]

{<font color = "red" size = "6">
(print: "Thaxted's Stamina " + (text: $MyStamina) + " Serpent's Stamina  " + (text: $SerpentStamina))
</font>}

{(either: "Thaxted finds a way though the serpent's defences...","Thaxted's attack is successful...","Moving like a tap dancer, Thaxted strikes the serpent...","Dodging the creature's wicked fangs, Thaxted delivers a good old punch...")

(if: $Attack > 1)[
And catches the creature with his knife...
]

(if: $SerpentStamina < 1)[
(go-to: "Beat Serpent")
]
}

[[Keep fighting|Fight Serpent]]

{<font color = "red" size = "6">
(print: "Thaxted's Stamina " + (text: $MyStamina) + " Serpent's Stamina " + (text: $SerpentStamina))
</font>}

{(either: "The serpent strikes at Thaxted...","In a blur of speed, the serpent attacks Thaxted...","The serpent moves like lightning and breaks through Thaxted's defences...","With open jaws, the serpent lashes out at Thaxted...")
(if: $SerpentAttack > 1)[
And catches him with its fangs...(if: $InfoFlag)[There is a dumbing sensation... The creature's fangs are poisoned...(set: $InfoFlag to false)]
]
(if: $MyStamina < 1)[
(go-to: "Beaten By Serpent")
]
(if: not $HoldingKnife and $KnifeFlag)[
<font color = "white">The knife is knocked from Thaxted's hand...(set:$KnifeFlag to false)</font>]}

[[Keep fighting...|Fight Serpent]]
